This is a little... \! Maybe it's no good anymore...

Luna... I'm sorry. I've come this far to help you... I thought I
was doing my best...

I was completely useless. In the end... I was powerless and
couldn't do anything. I was just a burden to you.

There is absolutely no way that's true. You are not a burden.
...Besides.

Do you know how much of a support you have been for me... If you
have seen my dream... You would understand, right? So please,
don't say such things...

Yeah... that's right. Even though you think so highly of me, it
would be disrespectful to you if I belittled myself...

If I say something like this again, I might be thought of as
saying something weird...

In 'my dream'... \! To embrace you, my beloved, and die
together... \! Isn't that a little romantic?

Y-You're right, it's 'weird' after all...! It's strange to be
like this at a time like this...!

But... I also thought for a moment. Dying in the dream of the
person I love... It's a little... romantic.
You understand...!? No, I'm so happy I could cry...!
Geez, don't make me laugh... You totally caught me off guard...

But, thank you... Maybe my feelings of unease have disappeared.
Will you... keep me locked away inside of you?

...Yes, I will keep you locked away. Forever in this world, just
you and me... Alone.
Ahaha... If Luna says so, then I feel relieved...
But... I'm a little scared. Will you stay by my side forever...?

That's not obvious at all. If you're not with me... my life up
until now would be meaningless.

You know... when I'm near Luna... I can't help but laugh, and
tears start to well up... I feel so, so relieved.
That's... I feel the same way. Hehe, we're on the same page, huh?
It feels like time has passed, huh.

In the end... I'm glad we could spend time together. I'm glad...
that I love you.
I also... love you. I'm glad.
Thank you... I love you so much... Luna....
Laura... Me? I have something I want to tell you...
I hate this kind of thing!

What should I say... this... It's a bit different from the
happiness I wanted to see...! It's too perverse for a child...
Hmm...

I wanted to experience the feeling of normal happiness...
Spending peaceful days together... And maybe even having a child
eventually... Kyaa!

I wanted to see that kind of thing! What...! Both of you feeling
a romantic connection to a double suicide. That's a bit too
adult, isn't it...!

Ahaha... that's right...! It seems like the two of you are
determined to die...

Let me forcefully show you normal happiness! If I do that, you
won't have any choice but to become happy...!

Hmm... For the two of you, huh... It's a bit heavy, but I guess
there's no helping it...

Ugh... It's so burdensome for both of you...! Making a child do
this kind of labor... It's a crime...!

Okay, this should be enough...! After this, I can just throw it
randomly, right?!
